    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 2nd level, as a standard action, a spiritualist can share the senses of her manifested phantom, hearing, seeing, smelling, tasting, and feeling everything her phantom does.</p>\n<p>She can use this ability a number of rounds per day equal to her spiritualist level, but those rounds do not need to be consecutive.</p>\n<p>There is no maximum range for this effect, but the phantom and the spiritualist must be on the same plane. The spiritualist can end this effect as a free action.</p>",
